BAT MASTERSON (1958-1961)  starring Gene Barry

307. High Card Loses    11/10/1960
When his friend is murdered, Bat agrees to undertake his unfinished business - delivering three mail-order brides to their new husbands.

308. Dakota Showdown    11/17/1960
Bat rides to the assistance of his friend, a sheriff, but arrives after the Dakota boys gun him down. The president of the town council asks Bat to step into the office, but Bat decides the job should go to another person.
